<mixertitle>GAP package MajoranaAlgebras</mixertitle>

<h2>A package for constructing Majorana algebras and representations</h2>
<p class="homelink">[<a href="https://MWhybrow92.github.io/MajoranaAlgebras/">WWW homepage</a>]</p>
<h4>Authors</h4>
<p><a href="https://markusp.morphism.de/">Markus Pfeiffer</a>, 
<a href="https://www.madeleinewhybrow.wordpress.com">Madeleine Whybrow</a></p>
<h4>Short Description</h4>
<p><![CDATA[MajoranaAlgebras is a package for constructing Majorana representations of finite groups. It also offers some functions to calculate with a constructed Majorana representation. The main constructive functions use the algorithm described in the preprint Constructing Majorana Representations (https://arxiv.org/abs/1803.10723) by Markus Pfeiffer and Madeleine Whybrow.]]>
</p>

<mixer part="extra" needed="no"/>

